<br>
No doubt, in higher level encounters, the 11 raw AC that Barbed BP gives me would make a bigger difference. However, as of right now, I am sticking with Iksar BP til I can save up money to buy the Barbed BP again (I sold the Barbed BP to buy a 30/36 War Lance, a good decision on my part, I &quot;think&quot; hehehe). <br>
<br>
